        p.lead BDD Analysis is a 2-day training in the analysis and collaboration aspects of Behaviour-Driven Development (BDD). It is a non-technical training for BAs, POs, developers and testers who want to learn how to create better executable specifications and living documentation.
        p.lead If your organisation is only using Cucumber for test automation, this training will equip you with the skills you need to start using it for executable specifications and living documentation as well.
